---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About MarkdownMaster — Free Online Markdown Editor"
  description="MarkdownMaster is a free, open-source online Markdown editor built for speed and privacy. Learn about the team, our mission, and how the tool works."
  canonical="https://markdownmaster.site/about/"
  jsonld={{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "AboutPage",
    "name": "About MarkdownMaster",
    "url": "https://markdownmaster.site/about/",
    "description": "MarkdownMaster is a free, open-source online Markdown editor built for speed and privacy. Learn about the team, our mission, and how the tool works.",
    "about": {
      "@type": "WebApplication",
      "name": "MarkdownMaster",
      "url": "https://markdownmaster.site",
      "description": "Free online Markdown editor with real-time preview, GitHub Flavored Markdown, and syntax highlighting. No sign-up required.",
      "applicationCategory": "DeveloperApplication",
      "operatingSystem": "Web",
      "offers": { "@type": "Offer", "price": "0" },
      "author": { "@type": "Person", "name": "KK Tian", "url": "https://github.com/tzhkai" }
    }
  }}
>
  <style>
    .page-wrap { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem 1.5rem; }
    .page-wrap h1 { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
    .page-wrap h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 0.5rem; color: var(--accent); }
    .page-wrap p { color: #cbd5e1; line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .page-wrap ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; color: #cbd5e1; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    .page-wrap li { margin: 0.3rem 0; }
    .team-card {
      background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px; padding: 1.2rem; margin: 1rem 0;
    }
    .team-card strong { color: var(--accent); }
  </style>

  <div class="page-wrap">
    <h1>About MarkdownMaster</h1>
    <p><em>Built for speed. Built for privacy. Built for you.</em></p>

    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>MarkdownMaster exists because most online Markdown editors are either slow, cluttered with ads, or require sign-up. We wanted a tool that loads instantly, previews in real time, and never asks for your email.</p>
    <p>Everything runs in your browser. No data leaves your device. No accounts, no tracking, no hidden costs.</p>

    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <p>MarkdownMaster is a <strong>client-side application</strong>. When you type on the left, a lightweight parser converts your text to formatted HTML on the right — all inside your browser. No server round-trips, no latency.</p>
    <p>We support <strong>GitHub Flavored Markdown (GFM)</strong> including tables, task lists, strikethrough, auto-links, and emoji shortcodes. Code blocks get syntax highlighting via Prism.js across 100+ languages.</p>

    <h2>Who Built This</h2>
    <div class="team-card">
      <p><strong>KK Tian</strong> — Creator &amp; Developer</p>
      <p>Independent developer focused on building fast, privacy-first web tools. MarkdownMaster is built with Astro, deployed on Cloudflare Pages, and open source on GitHub.</p>
      <p><a href="https://github.com/tzhkai" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent)">GitHub →</a> &middot;
      <a href="https://github.com/tzhkai/markdownmaster" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent)">Source code →</a></p>
    </div>

    <h2>Technology</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Astro</strong> — Static site generation with zero JavaScript runtime</li>
      <li><strong>Cloudflare Pages</strong> — Global edge deployment with instant cache</li>
      <li><strong>Prism.js</strong> — Syntax highlighting for 100+ languages</li>
      <li><strong>D1 (Cloudflare)</strong> — Edge database for dynamic content</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Open Source</h2>
    <p>MarkdownMaster is open source under the MIT license. The full source code is available on <a href="https://github.com/tzhkai/markdownmaster" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent)">GitHub</a>. Contributions, bug reports, and feature requests are welcome.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions or feedback? Open an issue on <a href="https://github.com/tzhkai/markdownmaster/issues" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--accent)">GitHub Issues</a> or reach out via email at <a href="mailto:tianzhenkai@gmail.com" style="color:var(--accent)">tianzhenkai@gmail.com</a>.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
